---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Services — Jodie Plant Marketing"
  description="Search & AI visibility, authority content, smart-stack paid media, and more. AI-enhanced marketing services for startups and tech companies."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="font-headline text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight">
          Marketing That Gets You Found
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          One senior marketer. Your entire account. Built on The Visibility Engine — a repeatable system to get you discovered by buyers (and by AI) at the moment of intent.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE VISIBILITY ENGINE -->
  <section id="visibility-engine" class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-navy">The Visibility Engine</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">
          AI-orchestrated marketing systems change the game. Instead of disconnected tactics, you get a unified engine that compounds over time. Every channel feeds every other channel.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 bg-light rounded-xl border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange text-white font-mono font-bold text-sm mb-4">1</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Discover</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Audit visibility, citations, gaps</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs font-mono text-orange">Free Visibility Snapshot</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-light rounded-xl border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange text-white font-mono font-bold text-sm mb-4">2</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Dominate</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Build search authority &amp; AI-citeable content</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs font-mono text-orange">SEO &middot; GEO &middot; Content</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-light rounded-xl border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange text-white font-mono font-bold text-sm mb-4">3</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Amplify</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Scale with paid, social, distribution</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs font-mono text-orange">Ads &middot; Social &middot; Email</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-light rounded-xl border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange text-white font-mono font-bold text-sm mb-4">4</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Optimize</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Measure, iterate, improve ROI</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs font-mono text-orange">Analytics &middot; Testing &middot; Reports</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-light">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-navy text-center">Services</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">Each service is enhanced by AI-orchestrated workflows — faster research, sharper optimization, better results.</p>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-8">
        <!-- Service 1: Search & AI Visibility -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 md:flex md:gap-8 md:items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m21 21-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 1 0 5.196 5.196a7.5 7.5 0 0 0 10.607 10.607Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Search &amp; AI Visibility <span class="text-sm font-normal text-muted">(SEO + GEO)</span></h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-orange font-medium italic">The AI difference: AI-powered keyword clustering, entity optimization, and real-time visibility monitoring across both traditional search and AI answer engines.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-muted text-sm">
              <li>• Technical SEO audit &amp; ongoing optimization</li>
              <li>• AI answer engine optimization (GEO)</li>
              <li>• Keyword strategy &amp; content roadmap</li>
              <li>• Link building &amp; authority development</li>
              <li>• Search visibility monitoring &amp; reporting</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-navy">Get found where buyers actually look — Google, ChatGPT, Perplexity, and AI Overviews.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 2: AI Marketing Systems -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 md:flex md:flex-row-reverse md:gap-8 md:items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09ZM18.259 8.715 18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455 2.456L21.75 6l-1.036.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455 2.456ZM16.894 20.567 16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423 1.423Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">AI Marketing Systems</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-orange font-medium italic">The AI difference: Custom AI workflows that automate research, content production, optimization, and reporting — giving you a team's output from a single strategist.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-muted text-sm">
              <li>• Custom AI workflow design &amp; implementation</li>
              <li>• Automated competitive monitoring</li>
              <li>• AI-enhanced content production pipelines</li>
              <li>• Marketing automation &amp; integration</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-navy">The infrastructure that makes everything else faster and sharper.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 3: Authority Content & AI Citation -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 md:flex md:gap-8 md:items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 0 0 6 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 1 6 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 0 1 6-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 0 18 18a8.967 8.967 0 0 0-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Authority Content &amp; AI Citation</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-orange font-medium italic">The AI difference: AI-accelerated research, content optimization for both human readers and AI extraction, and entity authority signals that compound over time.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-muted text-sm">
              <li>• Content strategy &amp; editorial planning</li>
              <li>• Blog posts, guides, and thought leadership</li>
              <li>• Content optimized for AI citation &amp; search</li>
              <li>• LinkedIn content strategy &amp; distribution</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-navy">Content that earns trust, builds authority, and gets cited — by humans and AI.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 4: Smart-Stack Paid Media -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 md:flex md:flex-row-reverse md:gap-8 md:items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 3 19.875v-6.75ZM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V8.625ZM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V4.125Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Smart-Stack Paid Media</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-orange font-medium italic">The AI difference: AI-powered bid optimization, creative testing at scale, and smart budget allocation across platforms that actually convert — not just Google and Meta.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-muted text-sm">
              <li>• Google, Meta, LinkedIn, Bing, Reddit ads</li>
              <li>• Smart budget allocation across platforms</li>
              <li>• Creative strategy &amp; A/B testing</li>
              <li>• Retargeting &amp; audience building</li>
              <li>• Monthly performance reporting</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-navy">Every dollar earns its place. No wasted spend on vanity impressions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 5: Fractional Marketing Leadership -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 md:flex md:gap-8 md:items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Fractional Marketing Leadership</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-orange font-medium italic">The AI difference: Senior marketing leadership enhanced by AI systems — strategy, execution, and reporting at the CMO level, without the CMO salary.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-muted text-sm">
              <li>• Marketing strategy &amp; roadmap development</li>
              <li>• Team &amp; vendor management</li>
              <li>• Budget planning &amp; allocation</li>
              <li>• Board-level reporting &amp; KPI frameworks</li>
              <li>• Hiring support &amp; marketing org design</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-navy">Think of me as your fractional CMO — embedded in your team, not an outside vendor.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 6: Social Media & Short-Form Video -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 md:flex md:flex-row-reverse md:gap-8 md:items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m15.75 10.5 4.72-4.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.28.53v11.38a.75.75 0 0 1-1.28.53l-4.72-4.72M4.5 18.75h9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25h-9A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 7.5v9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Social Media &amp; Short-Form Video</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-orange font-medium italic">The AI difference: AI-assisted content calendars, trend spotting, and caption optimization that keep you consistent without the full-time commitment.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-muted text-sm">
              <li>• LinkedIn, Twitter/X, and platform strategy</li>
              <li>• Content calendar &amp; scheduling</li>
              <li>• Short-form video strategy (Reels, TikTok, Shorts)</li>
              <li>• Community engagement playbooks</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-navy">Build a social presence that reinforces your brand — not one that dies after a month.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 7: Conversion Rate Optimization -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 md:flex md:gap-8 md:items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18 9 11.25l4.306 4.306a11.95 11.95 0 0 1 5.814-5.518l2.74-1.22m0 0-5.94-2.281m5.94 2.28-2.28 5.941" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Conversion Rate Optimization</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-orange font-medium italic">The AI difference: AI-powered A/B test prioritization, heatmap analysis, and conversion funnel optimization that compound your existing traffic.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-muted text-sm">
              <li>• Conversion audit &amp; opportunity analysis</li>
              <li>• A/B testing &amp; experimentation</li>
              <li>• Landing page optimization</li>
              <li>• Form &amp; CTA optimization</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-navy">A 20% improvement in conversion rate equals a 20% increase in your marketing budget — without spending another dollar on ads.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 8: Local Visibility & Reputation -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 md:flex md:flex-row-reverse md:gap-8 md:items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Local Visibility &amp; Reputation</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-orange font-medium italic">The AI difference: AI-monitored review sentiment, automated local listing management, and AI-citation optimization for local intent queries.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-muted text-sm">
              <li>• Google Business Profile optimization</li>
              <li>• Local SEO &amp; citation building</li>
              <li>• Review generation &amp; management</li>
              <li>• Local content strategy</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-navy">Dominate local search and build a reputation that brings customers to your door.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 9: Email Marketing & Owned Audience -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 md:flex md:gap-8 md:items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 19.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07-1.916V6.75" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Email Marketing &amp; Owned Audience</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-orange font-medium italic">The AI difference: AI-optimized send times, subject lines, and segmentation that turn your email list into a reliable revenue channel.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-muted text-sm">
              <li>• Email strategy &amp; automation setup</li>
              <li>• Nurture sequences &amp; drip campaigns</li>
              <li>• Newsletter design &amp; management</li>
              <li>• List building &amp; segmentation</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-navy">Build an owned audience that isn't dependent on algorithms or ad budgets.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Always Included -->
      <div class="mt-12 bg-navy/5 rounded-xl p-8 border border-navy/10">
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">What's Always Included: Growth Attribution &amp; AI Insights</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-muted">Every engagement includes analytics infrastructure, conversion tracking, and transparent monthly reporting. You'll always know what's working, what's not, and where your money goes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-navy text-center">Packages &amp; Pricing</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">Three tiers designed around where you are and where you want to go.</p>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Foundation -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Foundation</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">For startups ready to build their marketing engine</p>
          <p class="mt-4 font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-navy">From $1,500<span class="text-lg text-muted font-normal">/mo</span></p>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-muted flex-grow">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange">✓</span> SEO &amp; search visibility foundation</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange">✓</span> Content strategy &amp; 2 blog posts/month</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange">✓</span> Basic paid media management</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange">✓</span> Monthly reporting &amp; analytics</li>
