            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange">✓</span> Social media management</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange">✓</span> Bi-weekly strategy calls</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-muted">Who it's for: Series A–B. Ready to invest in growth.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full px-6 py-3 bg-orange text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-orange/90 transition-colors min-h-[44px]">
            Get Started
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Authority -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Authority <span class="text-sm font-normal text-muted">/ Fractional CMO</span></h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">Full marketing leadership without the full-time hire</p>
          <p class="mt-4 font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-navy">From $4,500<span class="text-lg text-muted font-normal">/mo</span></p>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-muted flex-grow">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange">✓</span> Everything in Growth</li>
